    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">
      You must achieve a <strong>10% profit target</strong> with no time limit, using a balance-based (static) drawdown model. Both a maximum daily drawdown and a maximum overall drawdown apply, and breaching either results in account failure.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      While CTI markets scaling across its programs, One Step accounts are effectively capped at <strong>$200,000 per account</strong>. This means the widely promoted $4 million scaling potential does not apply to this challenge type.
    </p>

