    </p>
    <p class="mb-3">
      In Phase One, you must reach a <strong>10% profit target</strong>, followed by <strong>5%</strong> in Phase Two, while remaining within the same balance-based drawdown limits. There is no time limit, and CTI requires a minimum number of profitable trading days in each phase.
