    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Profit share starts at around <strong>50%</strong> — significantly lower than evaluation-based programs — and increases through scaling milestones, reaching up to 100% at higher funding levels. The early-stage profit split is notably lower than most competing instant funding firms.
    </p>

